prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon slice of cherry pie, looking slightly tipsy and wearing a tiny, askew party hat, is cheekily winking. It's holding a single lit birthday candle. Next to it, a whole, perfect cherry pie looks on with a slightly exasperated expression. Splatters of cherry filling and buttery crust crumbs are scattered playfully around them. Centered in the middle of the card, the text "hope your birthday is as easy as pie" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds, especially around the edges of the pie and the filling splatters.
